msgid "You're done."
msgstr "你完成了。"

msgid "Good work."
msgstr "做的好。"

msgid "What now?"
msgstr "现在怎么办？"

msgid "Now, all of these objects need to be burned in the correct order."
msgstr "现在，按照正确的顺序烧毁这些物品。"

msgid "What's the order?"
msgstr "怎样的顺序？"

msgid "That's for you to figure out. The hands over there might provide a clue."
msgstr "这就得你自己弄清楚了。那边的手或许会给你提供线索。"

msgid "I see..."
msgstr "嗯..."

msgid "Make sure you have a way to light the fireplace as well."
msgstr "同时，确保你有点燃壁炉的方法。"

msgid "Oh, that's true..."
msgstr "哦，对..."

msgid "(Are there any places I haven't checked yet...?)"
msgstr "（这里是不是还有我没调查过的地方...？）"

msgid "Lastly... this whole thing tends to culminate with candles going out."
msgstr "最后... 这一切都会以蜡烛的熄灭而告终。"

msgid "Therefore, if you see any candles, put them out."
msgstr "因此，如果你看到蜡烛，就将它熄灭吧。"

msgid "Understood."
msgstr "明白了。"

msgid "One more thing."
msgstr "还有一件事。"

msgid "I couldn't help but notice how weak you look."
msgstr "我不禁注意到，你看起来是那么的弱小。"

msgid "The challenges ahead might be beyond your capabilities."
msgstr "未来的挑战可能会超出你的能力范围。"

msgid "There's an object inside my old hiding spot that can help with that."
msgstr "在我之前的藏身之处，有一个东西能帮到你。"

msgid "Spider is just dangling there."
msgstr "蜘蛛在那里晃来晃去。"

msgid "Psst..."
msgstr "嘶..."

msgid "Over here."
msgstr "来这里。"

msgid "Here. On the wall."
msgstr "这里。墙上。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.event_spider.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "Spider...?"
msgstr "蜘蛛...？"

msgid "Yes."
msgstr "没错。"

msgid "Is that really you?"
msgstr "真的是你吗？"

msgid "Huh... you really meant it when you said you talked to a spider."
msgstr "呃...原来你说你和蜘蛛讲话的事情是真的啊。"

msgid "He looked different last time, but it's still basically a spider."
msgstr "他看起来和上次很不一样，但是它还是蜘蛛。"

msgid "Oh. There's two of you now."
msgstr "哦。现在你们有两个人了。"

msgid "Well, no matter."
msgstr "好吧，没关系。"

msgid "You look... different."
msgstr "你看起来...很不一样"

msgid "...But I can't quite put my finger on it."
msgstr "...但是我怕说的又不着边际。"

msgid "I don't appreciate your humor."
msgstr "我无法理解你的幽默。"

msgid "Miss Knives discovered my hiding spot."
msgstr "莉刃小姐发现了我的藏身之处。"

msgid "She's not fond of my presence."
msgstr "她不希望我出现。"

msgid "So she turned me into... this."
msgstr "所以她把我变成了...这样。"

msgid "It's pathetic."
msgstr "真是可悲。"

msgid "Damn, she must have crazy powers."
msgstr "天呐，她的力量也太强大了吧。"

msgid "Is she really that powerful?"
msgstr "她真的有这么强大吗？"

msgid "Not quite."
msgstr "并不。"

msgid "You both must have had some time to look around this place by now."
msgstr "你们两个肯定已经在这里四处转过了吧。"

msgid "You must have had some time to look around this place by now."
msgstr "你肯定已经在这里四处转过了吧。"

msgid "Did you figure out anything strange?"
msgstr "没有发现什么奇怪的事情吗？"

msgid "You mean aside from... everything?"
msgstr "你是说... 这里的一切吗？"

msgid "Kind of a tall order, pal."
msgstr "朋友，你对我们要求太高了。"

msgid "...Well..."
msgstr "...好吧..."

msgid "The location of this house is strange."
msgstr "这间房子的所在之处很奇怪。"

msgid "The walls are filled with creepy paintings."
msgstr "墙上挂满了可怕的画像。"

msgid "It's all very purple, I guess."
msgstr "这里颜色很紫，我感觉。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.event_spider.dlg.ch1_spider"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "...Maybe humans are just slow."
msgstr "...可能人类都会慢一拍吧。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.event_spider.dlg.sai"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "None of what you're seeing is real."
msgstr "你所见的一切皆非真实。"

msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "啊？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.event_spider.dlg.lacie"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "什么？"

msgid "Miss Knives is a strange case."
msgstr "莉刃小姐是个怪人。"

msgid "She created this place out of her own desires."
msgstr "她凭自己的力量创造了这个地方。"

msgid "But the house doesn't actually exist."
msgstr "但是这间房子其实并不存在。"

msgid "Convenient."
msgstr "这就解释得通了。"

msgid "So then... it's an illusion?"
msgstr "所以说...这是一个幻象？"

msgid "To an extent, yes."
msgstr "某种程度上，是的。"

msgid "That's also why I look like this."
msgstr "这也就是为什么我看起来像这样。"

msgid "Miss Knives only sees what she wants to see."
msgstr "莉刃小姐只看她想看见的东西。"

msgid "So she sees you as... a little spider on the wall?"
msgstr "所以她把你看作了...一只墙上的小蜘蛛？"

msgid "It would seem so."
msgstr "看来是的。"

msgid "I see."
msgstr "嗯。"

msgid "Then... to escape..."
msgstr "接着...关于逃脱的事情..."

msgid "You have to break the illusion."
msgstr "你需要打破幻象。"

msgid "Remind her who she is."
msgstr "让她记起自己是谁。"

msgid "Or rather... who she isn't."
msgstr "又或者说...她不是谁。"

msgid "That's where those objects you need to collect come into play."
msgstr "这就是你要去收集的物品发挥作用的时候了。"

msgid "They seem to have some sort of connection to her memories."
msgstr "它们看起来与她的记忆有某种联系。"

msgid "Once you find and unseal them all, come back and see me."
msgstr "一旦你找到并解封了所有物品，就回来找我吧。"

msgid "If you need help with the burning order..."
msgstr "如果你想知道燃烧的顺序..."

msgid "The painting with the hands might provide you with a hint."
msgstr "那幅画着手的画作或许会给你一些提示。"

msgid "That seems to be already unsealed."
msgstr "那看起来已经被解封了。"

msgid "You don't need to do anything else with it."
msgstr "你已经不用对它做什么了。"

msgid "(The hands reject the item... it needs to be unsealed first.)"
msgstr "（这双手拒绝了这件物品...需要先解封它。）"

msgid "My mother got worse one day."
msgstr "有一天，我母亲病情加重了。"

msgid "Father thinks she might die."
msgstr "父亲觉得她可能会死。"

msgid "I don't want mom to die."
msgstr "但我不想妈妈死。"

msgid "I brought her a cold compress to lower the fever."
msgstr "我给她带了一块降温用的冷敷布。"

msgid "Mother always said that water provides the best healing."
msgstr "母亲总说，水是最好的良药。"

msgid "That night, I said a prayer to try to help her."
msgstr "那一夜，我祈祷能帮助她。"

msgid "I wished for her to get better, and I wished for our family to go back to normal, at least."
msgstr "我希望她变得更好，最起码，我希望我们的家庭能够走回正轨。"

msgid "The [color=#90EE90]third blessing[/color] came as a surprise to everyone in the village."
msgstr "[color=#90EE90]第三件祝福[/color]让村子里的每个人都大吃一惊。"

msgid "The morning after my prayer, my mother was out of bed, and cooking."
msgstr "我做完祷告的第二天早上，我的母亲就能下床做饭了。"

msgid "She said she felt much better, she even had strength to go to the market."
msgstr "她说她感觉好多了，她甚至有力气去集市买东西了。"

msgid "You see? The cold compress did the job!"
msgstr "看到了吗？这块冷敷布做到了！"

msgid "Clean water is the purest thing we have."
msgstr "清水是我们拥有的，最纯净的事物。"

msgid "Are you sure you should be out of bed?"
msgstr "你确定你要从床上下来吗？"

msgid "This is the best I've felt in years."
msgstr "这是我这几年感觉最好的一次了。"

msgid "But... the doctor said..."
msgstr "但是...医生说..."

msgid "I'm sure he was just wrong."
msgstr "我觉得他可能是误诊了。"

msgid "You know, medicine isn't always entirely accurate."
msgstr "你知道的，医学并不总是完全准确的。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_compress_on_holder.dlg.mk"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "No more than two days later, some adults knocked at the door."
msgstr "没过两天，一些大人就来敲我家的门。"

msgid "They took my mother. They called her a witch."
msgstr "他们带走了我的母亲。他们把她叫做女巫。"

msgid "They claimed she used her powers to get cured of a deadly illness."
msgstr "他们声称她用她的力量治愈了一种绝症。"

msgid "They said the village needs to be cleansed, and that witch hunts were important for this."
msgstr "他们认为这个村庄需要被净化，而狩猎女巫是最重要的一环。"

msgid "The next day, my mother was burned at the stake."
msgstr "第二天，我母亲被烧死在火刑柱上。"

msgid "Everyone watched, and everyone cheered, as she died slowly, for a sin she did not commit."
msgstr "每个人都在旁观着，每个人都在欢呼着，她慢慢地死去，只因她从未犯下的罪过。"

msgid "This was the first time I wished that I couldn't see anymore."
msgstr "这是我第一次希望自己什么也看不见。"

msgid "Have you somehow missed the large painting that's lacking eyes?"
msgstr "你是不是错过了一幅缺少眼睛的大型画作？"

msgid "The [color=#90EE90]fourth blessing[/color] was something I would never wish for."
msgstr "[color=#90EE90]第四件祝福[/color]是我从未期许之物。"

msgid "Give it back!"
msgstr "还给我！"

msgid "How'd you get your hands on such an expensive-looking sketchbook, huh?"
msgstr "你是怎么搞到这么贵的绘画本的？"

msgid "Let's see..."
msgstr "让我看看..."

msgid "Stop! Just give it to me!"
msgstr "别！把它还给我吧！"

msgid "What the heck is this?"
msgstr "这是什么鬼东西？"

msgid "They flipped through the pages of my sketchbook, and their faces got an awful ghostly white."
msgstr "他们一页页翻动着我的绘画本，脸色变得像幽灵般惨白。"

msgid "Is she a witch?"
msgstr "难道她是女巫？"

msgid "What are those?"
msgstr "请问这些是什么？"

msgid "I didn't draw that!"
msgstr "不是我画的！"

msgid "Hey, I didn't know you were a witch."
msgstr "嘿，我之前不知道你其实是个女巫啊。"

msgid "I'm not!!!"
msgstr "我不是！！！"

msgid "Pages and pages of creepy drawings."
msgstr "一页又一页恐怖的绘画。"

msgid "What is this? Some kind of curse casting shit?"
msgstr "这是什么？某种狗屁诅咒吗？"

msgid "I didn't make them! I don't know where they came from!"
msgstr "不是我画的！我也不知道它们从哪来的！"

msgid "It's the truth. Why didn't they believe me?"
msgstr "这就是真相。为什么他们不相信我？"

msgid "STOP! WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!?"
msgstr "停下！你们在做什么？！？"

msgid "You're just a filthy witch!"
msgstr "你就是个肮脏的女巫！"

msgid "I'm reporting you, you won't be needing this!"
msgstr "我要告发你，你不需要这本了！"

msgid "PLEASE DON'T BREAK IT!"
msgstr "求你们不要把它弄坏！"

msgid "You don't even need all of these colors."
msgstr "你甚至不需要这些颜料。"

msgid "Nothing but black."
msgstr "你只配用黑的。"

msgid "You were never supposed to see anything but darkness anyway."
msgstr "你本来就不应该看到黑暗以外的任何东西。"

msgid "Blind freak."
msgstr "瞎子。"

msgid "Please stop... Give them back..."
msgstr "求你停下... 把它还给我..."

msgid "Aww.. poor little crybaby."
msgstr "呜... 真是可怜的爱哭鬼啊。"

msgid "I'm gonna report you."
msgstr "我要去告发你。"

msgid "Father will be so proud, I caught my own witch."
msgstr "父亲会很骄傲的，因为我抓到女巫了。"

msgid "I'm not a witch..."
msgstr "我不是女巫..."

msgid "I swear I'm not..."
msgstr "我发誓我不是..."

msgid "No! Don't!!!! Please!!!"
msgstr "不！不要！！！！求你们了！！！"

msgid "(Stop, please stop...)"
msgstr "（停下，求你们停下...）"

msgid "(Please stop...)"
msgstr "（求你们停下...）"

msgid "(What did I do to you...?)"
msgstr "（我对你们做了什么吗...？）"

msgid "(Please stop.......)"
msgstr "（求你们停下.......）"

msgid "I hate them. I hate my life. Why is this happening to me?"
msgstr "我讨厌他们。我讨厌自己的人生。为什么要这样对我？"

msgid "Soon enough, the boy dropped the sketchbook."
msgstr "过了一会儿，那本绘画本从男孩那里掉了下来。"

msgid "My eyes were focused on the crumpled pages of my sketchbook hitting the ground, so I didn't see it until someone screamed."
msgstr "我的眼睛注视着绘画本上被摔得皱巴巴的纸张，直到有人尖叫起来，我才看到那个东西。"

msgid "...!?"
msgstr "...！？"

msgid "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHHHHHHHHH!!!!"
msgstr "啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！！！！"

msgid "The boy's right leg twisted almost 360 degrees, as if it was some form of nightmarish witchcraft."
msgstr "男孩的右腿被拧转了约360度，仿佛是某种噩梦般的巫术。"

msgid "Then it twisted again."
msgstr "接着，又拧转了一遍。"

msgid "Something broke in his leg, and he fell down, writhing in pain."
msgstr "他的腿断了，倒了下去，痛苦地扭动着。"

msgid "I couldn't understand what I was seeing."
msgstr "我无法理解我所见到的东西。"

msgid "Y-you... what did you do to his leg?!?"
msgstr "你—你...你对他的腿做了什么？！？"

msgid "N-Nothing I didn't even touch him..."
msgstr "什—什么也没做，我甚至都碰不到他..."

msgid "AAAAAAAAGGGHHHH! IT HURTS!!!!"
msgstr "啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！好痛！！！！"

msgid "Call someone! We need help! HELP!!!"
msgstr "叫人来！我们需要帮助！救命啊！！！"

msgid "YOU'RE A WITCH!! YOU'RE A WITCH!!!"
msgstr "你是个女巫！！你是个女巫！！！"

msgid "I WILL DESTROY YOU!!!! YOU'LL BE BURNED!!!!"
msgstr "我会消灭你！！！！你会被活活烧死！！！！"

msgid "................."
msgstr "................."

msgid "BURN IN HELL!!!"
msgstr "在地狱里燃烧吧！！！"

msgid "The adults came and took him away."
msgstr "大人们来了，把他带走了。"

msgid "When I finally lifted my gaze from the dirt below my fingers, Iris was standing in front of me."
msgstr "当我终于把目光从指缝间的泥土上移开时，艾瑞丝正站在我的面前。"

msgid "My heart sank... Did she see what happened?"
msgstr "我的心沉了下来... 她看见刚才发生了什么吗？"

msgid "...A-Are you alright...?"
msgstr "...你—你还好吗...？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_foot_on_holder.dlg.mk"
msgid "............"
msgstr "............"

msgid "I-I... You didn't do that to his leg, right?"
msgstr "我—我...他的腿不是你弄的吧？"

msgid "No! Of course I didn't!"
msgstr "不是！当然不是我！"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_foot_on_holder.dlg.chara1"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "O-Okay."
msgstr "好—好的。"

msgid "...I... Why are you here?"
msgstr "...我... 为什么你在这里？"

msgid "Um... I came because... my parents said..."
msgstr "呃...我来这里是因为...我父母说..."

msgid "...That I'm not allowed to see you anymore."
msgstr "...我不能再见你了。"

msgid "Take ${item:ch1.mk_jar} x3?"
msgstr "要取走${item:ch1.mk_jar} x3吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_jars_get.choice.Take ${item:ch1.mk_jar} x3?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_jars_get.choice.Take ${item:ch1.mk_jar} x3?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "You may use that on the canvas over there."
msgstr "你也许能在那边的画布上使用。"

msgid "That's the right idea, I think."
msgstr "我想你做的是对的。"

msgid "What should I be doing with these?"
msgstr "我应该怎么处理这些东西？"

msgid "They're probably related to that canvas over there."
msgstr "它们或许与那边的画布有关。"

msgid "Maybe you use them to make paint."
msgstr "也许你能用它们来做颜料。"

msgid "That's the key to the bedroom."
msgstr "这是前往卧室的钥匙。"

msgid "Oh... I don't need this anymore."
msgstr "哦...那看来我不需要这个了。"

msgid "That's a key to the cages."
msgstr "这是一把笼子的钥匙。"

msgid "I see you don't need it anymore."
msgstr "我看你已经不需要了。"

msgid "I can take that off your hands."
msgstr "把它给我吧。"

msgid "Oh... I see."
msgstr "哦...好的。"

msgid "That's the key to this room."
msgstr "这是这个房间的钥匙。"

msgid "I shall get rid of it, given that you already made it in."
msgstr "既然你已经进来了，我就把它扔掉吧。"

msgid "After the incident with that boy's leg, the authorities knocked at our door again."
msgstr "那次男孩的腿的事故发生后，当局再次敲响了我家的门。"

msgid "\"Your daughter is a witch\" they said to my father."
msgstr "“你的女儿是个女巫。”它们这么跟我的父亲说道。"

msgid "They talked about how I hurt that boy, how my mother healed from a fatal illness, how my eyesight came back."
msgstr "他们谈及了我如何伤害那个男孩、我的母亲如何治愈绝症以及我的视力如何恢复的内容。"

msgid "They told us both me and my father are accused of witchcraft."
msgstr "他们告诉我们，我和我父亲都被指控使用巫术。"

msgid "T-That's nonsense! What are you talking about??"
msgstr "这—这完全没道理啊！你们在说什么？？"

msgid "The whole family needs to be cleansed."
msgstr "这个家族需要被净化。"

msgid "Your daughter will be tried for witchcraft, and due to your ties to her, you will be as well."
msgstr "你的女儿会因巫术受审，由于你和她的亲缘关系，你也要。"

msgid "H-Hold on... Wait... You've got it all wrong. She's not my daughter."
msgstr "慢—慢着... 等一下... 你们都搞错了。她不是我的女儿"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_knife_on_holder.dlg.mk"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "I merely found her on the streets, she does not share my blood."
msgstr "我只是在街上捡到了她，她和我没有血缘关系的。"

msgid "(...Father...)"
msgstr "（...爸爸...）"

msgid "Take him."
msgstr "带走他。"

msgid "N-NO NO! PLEASE! I HAVE NOTHING TO DO WITH THIS!"
msgstr "不—不要，不要！求你们了！我真的什么也没做！"

msgid "When the men walked in the house, my father ran towards the back door."
msgstr "当这些人走进屋子的时候，我的父亲直奔后门。"

msgid "He was frantically bumping into the furniture to reach it."
msgstr "他疯狂地撞开家具，想要到那里去。"

msgid "Find the girl."
msgstr "找到那个女孩。"

msgid "And burn his body."
msgstr "然后把他的尸体烧了吧。"

msgid "Burn the whole house, it's cursed."
msgstr "把这栋房子也烧了，它已经被诅咒了。"

msgid "My father's blood ran down the hallway like a small river stream."
msgstr "父亲的鲜血像溪流一般流过走廊。"

msgid "It seeped into the cracks of the broken floorboards."
msgstr "渗入了破损地板的缝隙中。"

msgid "This is all that boy's fault."
msgstr "这都是那个男孩的错。"

msgid "The prison cell was cold, and dark."
msgstr "监狱里很冷，很暗。"

msgid "There was nobody else there with me, except for the occasional rat."
msgstr "这里没有人陪着我，除了偶尔出现的老鼠。"

msgid "People always said rats are dirty and dangerous."
msgstr "人们总说老鼠肮脏且危险。"

msgid "But at that moment, I appreciated the company."
msgstr "而这时，我很感激有它的陪伴。"

msgid "The adults told me my execution will be the following morning."
msgstr "大人们告诉我，我的死刑就在明天早上。"

msgid "They said I will be burned in order to purify the village."
msgstr "他们说我会被火刑，以净化村庄。"

msgid "What does that even mean? Purify the village..."
msgstr "这是什么意思？净化村庄..."

msgid "I was alone with my thoughts for what felt like hours before someone came by."
msgstr "我独自沉思了好几个小时，直到有人走了过来。"

msgid "Hey..."
msgstr "嘿..."

msgid "Iris...?"
msgstr "艾瑞丝...？"

msgid "(Will I get out of here...??)"
msgstr "（我能出去了吗...？？）"

msgid "Um... listen... I'm so sorry...!"
msgstr "呃... 听着... 我很抱歉...！"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_knife_on_holder.dlg.mk"
msgid "...?"
msgstr "...？"

msgid "I-... I told my dad about everything..."
msgstr "我—...我把一切都告诉了我爸爸..."

msgid "What...?"
msgstr "什么...？"

msgid "(...No way...)"
msgstr "（...怎么可能...）"

msgid "I... I thought if you might really be a witch, he could protect you...."
msgstr "我... 我以为你是女巫的话，他会保护你的..."

msgid "B-Because he knew we were friends!"
msgstr "因—因为他知道我们是朋友！"

msgid "I'm sorry... I did this...!"
msgstr "我很抱歉... 我做了这种事...！"

msgid "I didn't know he would kill your dad... and... and you..."
msgstr "我不知道他会杀了你爸爸... 还有... 还有你..."

msgid "Please..."
msgstr "请..."

msgid "Please take this knife..."
msgstr "请收下这把刀..."

msgid "P-please... please use it... before they kill you."
msgstr "请—请你... 请你在他们杀了你之前... 用它了结吧。"

msgid "You'll be better off if you end it this way...!"
msgstr "这样死的话，你会更好受一些...！"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_knife_on_holder.dlg.mk"
msgid "............"
msgstr "............"

msgid "What's happening?"
msgstr "发生了什么？"

msgid "Why would she tell me something like this?"
msgstr "为什么她要告诉我这种事情？"

msgid "What's going on?"
msgstr "到底怎么了？"

msgid "I-I love you and... father said burning is slow and painful...!!"
msgstr "我—我爱你，还有...父亲说火刑又慢又痛苦...！！"

msgid "You're better off doing it this way..!"
msgstr "你这样死的话会更好..！"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_knife_on_holder.dlg.mk"
msgid "....."
msgstr "....."

msgid "You're asking me to kill myself..?"
msgstr "你在求我自杀吗..？"

msgid "Y-Yes... because... I still care about you...!"
msgstr "对—对...因为...我还关心着你...！"

msgid "Is this what you call... care?"
msgstr "这就是你所谓的...关心？"

msgid "I didn't know that my vision would get blurry if I cry."
msgstr "我曾不知，我的视线会因为哭泣而变得模糊。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_knife_on_spider.dlg.lacie"
msgid "I need help with this."
msgstr "我需要帮忙。"

msgid "Ah, this is a knife."
msgstr "啊，这是一把刀。"

msgid "You might have to draw some blood to unseal it."
msgstr "你可能需要在上面涂一点血才能解封。"

msgid "Are you brave enough to cut yourself?"
msgstr "你有勇气自残吗？"

msgid "Why should I cut myself?"
msgstr "为什么我要自残啊？"

msgid "I don't see who else you could cut."
msgstr "因为我没见到有谁可以给你划一刀啊。"

msgid "I could cut you instead."
msgstr "我可以划你一刀。"

msgid "You'll never aim properly."
msgstr "你瞄不准的。"

msgid "Your aim is terrible."
msgstr "你的瞄法太差了。"

msgid "Perhaps there are advantages to being small after all."
msgstr "可能这就是变小的好处吧。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_knife_on_spider.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "You're not skilled enough for that."
msgstr "你的技术还不够熟练。"

msgid "(The hands reject the item... they're scared of it.)"
msgstr "（这双手拒绝了这件物品...它们可能怕它。）"

msgid "That should serve you well in lighting the fireplace."
msgstr "这应该方便你点燃壁炉了。"

msgid "My life is below average."
msgstr "我的生活很不幸。"

msgid "I've been blind since I was a baby, so my parents thought of abandoning me."
msgstr "我自小就是瞎子，所以我的父母产生了弃养我的想法。"

msgid "\"A blind child cannot help the family\" they said. \"Especially not a girl.\""
msgstr "“一个盲孩分担不了家庭事物，”他们说。“特别是女孩子。”"

msgid "But my mother says they loved me so much that they wanted to give me a chance."
msgstr "但是我的母亲说他们十分疼爱我，以至于他们想给我一次机会。"

msgid "Right now, I manage just fine."
msgstr "现在，我把一切都处理得很好。"

msgid "I do my chores, I go to the market, I help with the vegetable garden."
msgstr "我能做家务、去市场买菜、帮菜园干活。"

msgid "Mother is sick, so she's always in bed."
msgstr "母亲生病了，所以她一直躺在床上。"

msgid "The doctor says she might be like this for the rest of her life."
msgstr "医生说她可能今后都得像这样了。"

msgid "Every day, I go meet my friend at the riverbank."
msgstr "每天，我都会去河边见我的朋友。"

msgid "Iris is always talking excitedly about everything you could find outside of the village."
msgstr "艾瑞丝总是兴奋地谈论着村外的一切。"

msgid "She makes the world sound so bright."
msgstr "她使这个世界听上去如此美好。"

msgid "We made a deal, that when we turn 14, we'll run away together, and travel to mountains and seas."
msgstr "我们说好了，等到14岁那年，我们就一起离家出走，去游山玩水。"

msgid "But I was actually fine with a simple life. The bare minimum was enough, as long as I had Iris."
msgstr "但其实我对现在简单的生活很满意。只要有艾瑞丝在，最基本的生活就已经足够了。"

msgid "If there's one thing I wanted..."
msgstr "如果非要说有什么想要的..."

msgid "It was just to be able to see her."
msgstr "那就是，我想能够看见她。"

msgid "The [color=#90EE90]first blessing[/color] changed the course of my life."
msgstr "[color=#90EE90]第一件祝福[/color]改变了我的人生轨迹。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_mirror_on_holder.dlg.mk"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "........."
msgstr "........."

msgid "I couldn't calm my breathing."
msgstr "我无法平静自己的呼吸。"

msgid "I woke up one morning and I could see."
msgstr "一天早上醒来，我发现自己能够看见东西了。"

msgid "I saw shapes, and colors, and my parents."
msgstr "我能看到形状，看到色彩，看见我的父母。"

msgid "I saw the broken dining table."
msgstr "我能看见破损的餐桌。"

msgid "I saw the weeds in the vegetable garden."
msgstr "我能看到菜园里长满杂草。"

msgid "I saw the chipped cup that I drank from."
msgstr "我能看到我喝水的杯子碎了。"

msgid "I saw my wrinkled clothes."
msgstr "我能看见自己皱巴巴的衣服。"

msgid "Despite not having much, they were the most beautiful things I laid my eyes on."
msgstr "尽管能看到的东西不多，但它们却是我眼中最美的事物。"

msgid "I couldn't say the same about my reflection."
msgstr "但我对自己镜中的倒影却不能这么说。"

msgid "(Have I always looked like this?)"
msgstr "（我看起来一直是这个样子吗？）"

msgid "(Were my eyes always so... bland?)"
msgstr "（我的眼睛一直都这么...死板吗？）"

msgid "(Was my hair always so... dull?)"
msgstr "（我的头发一直都这么...粗糙吗？）"

msgid "My parents gradually grew distant."
msgstr "我的父母渐渐地疏远了我。"

msgid "People in the village stared at me, and whispered behind my back."
msgstr "村庄里的人都盯着我看，在我的背后说悄悄话。"

msgid "Why did they seem scared of me?"
msgstr "为什么他们这么怕我？"

msgid "Iris said she's a little nervous around me, but she was really happy that I got my eyesight."
msgstr "艾瑞丝说她在我身边时有些小紧张，但她还是很庆幸我拥有了视力。"

msgid "She called it a miracle."
msgstr "她把这称作奇迹。"

msgid "My parents started avoiding me."
msgstr "我的父母开始躲避我。"

msgid "When I spoke to them, they always tried to brush me away."
msgstr "当我和他们说话时，他们总是试图把我赶走。"

msgid "The only times their tired eyes met mine, I only saw hatred in them."
msgstr "他们疲惫的眼神与我相对时，我只从中看到了仇恨。"

msgid "Did they always look at me this way?"
msgstr "他们一直都是这样看我的吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_mirror_on_spider.dlg.lacie"
msgid "I need help with this."
msgstr "我需要帮忙。"

msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr "嗯......"

msgid "Have you tried simply looking at it?"
msgstr "你有没有试过简单地看它一眼？"

msgid "(The hands reject the item... it is irrelevant to them.)"
msgstr "（这双手拒绝了这件物品...这与它无关。）"

msgid "With your masterpiece complete, the canvas turns into a sketchbook."
msgstr "随着你杰作的完成，画布变成了一本绘图本。"

msgid "The pigment doesn't stick on its own..."
msgstr "单单只有颜料粉的话沾不上去..."

msgid "You soak the rag in the pool..."
msgstr "你在池子里洗了洗抹布..."

msgid "It's already wet enough."
msgstr "已经足够湿了。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_rag_on_spider.dlg.lacie"
msgid "I need help with this."
msgstr "我需要帮忙。"

msgid "A dry piece of cloth?"
msgstr "一块干布？"

msgid "Try moisturizing it."
msgstr "试着打湿它。"

msgid "The [color=#90EE90]second blessing[/color] came as a gift."
msgstr "[color=#90EE90]第二件祝福[/color]是一件礼物。"

msgid "I always met Iris out by the river, and we sat and talked for hours."
msgstr "我常在河边与艾瑞丝见面，我们会坐着交谈好几个小时。"

msgid "She told me all about the things I couldn't see."
msgstr "她告诉了我所有我看不到的东西。"

msgid "But it was different now."
msgstr "但是现在不一样了。"

msgid "She spoke with such happiness and excitement."
msgstr "她的话语中充满了幸福和兴奋。"

msgid "I couldn't take my eyes off of her."
msgstr "而我目不转睛地注视着她。"

msgid "So to celebrate this miracle..."
msgstr "所以，为了庆祝这一场奇迹..."

msgid "I got you something!"
msgstr "我给你带了个东西！"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.item_sketchbook_on_holder.dlg.mk"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "什么？"

msgid "For me?"
msgstr "给我吗？"

msgid "Of course! Your eyes work now! It's amazing! We have to celebrate!"
msgstr "当然啦！你能看见东西了！这太棒了！我们要庆祝一下！"

msgid "So... I stole this from my family..."
msgstr "所以...我从家里偷了这个..."

msgid "But shh!"
msgstr "但是，嘘！"

msgid "Don't tell!"
msgstr "别告诉大家！"

msgid "Wha-.."
msgstr "什—.."

msgid "Iris! A sketchbook and paints are... so expensive...!"
msgstr "艾瑞丝！绘画本和颜料都...很贵的诶...!"

msgid "H-How...? Why...?"
msgstr "怎—怎么...？为什么...？"

msgid "You always said you wanted to paint! I believe in you!"
msgstr "你一直说你想画画！我相信你！"

msgid "I'm so excited to see what you'll come up with!"
msgstr "我很期待看到你的作品！"

msgid "I couldn't believe it! My very own sketchbook and watercolors!"
msgstr "我简直不敢相信！属于我自己的绘画本和水彩！"

msgid "There were so many things I could paint!"
msgstr "有太多的东西可以画了！"

msgid "Mother was always bedridden, so I made a habit of showing her my paintings."
msgstr "母亲总是卧病在床，所以我养成了给她看我的画的习惯。"

msgid "I started with trees and objects."
msgstr "我从树木和小物件开始学。"

msgid "But I took a liking to portraits of people."
msgstr "但我对人物的肖像画情有独钟。"

msgid "They all have such distinct, beautiful faces."
msgstr "每个人都有独特而美丽的面孔。"

msgid "After only 2 days, I had already made 8 portraits!"
msgstr "仅仅过了两天，我就画了八幅肖像画！"

msgid "But when I flipped to the next page... a different kind of portrait filled the brown paper."
msgstr "但当我翻到下一页时...牛皮纸上出现了一幅与众不同的肖像。"

msgid "It was all painted in black, and it was twisted and scary."
msgstr "它全身漆黑，扭曲而可怖。"

msgid "I hadn't painted this..."
msgstr "这不是我画的..."

msgid "I didn't even know who this person- or... creature, was."
msgstr "我甚至都不知道这是谁—或者说...什么生物。"

msgid "Every morning after that, I found new distorted portraits in the pages, but I never remembered painting them."
msgstr "之后的每个早晨，我都会在书页中发现新的扭曲的肖像，但我从来不记得我画过它们。"

msgid "A bookshelf full of coloring books, and other children's books."
msgstr "书架上摆满了绘本和其他儿童读物。"

msgid "A bookshelf full of books about painting."
msgstr "书架上摆满了关于绘画的书籍。"

msgid "One of them stands out. Read a passage?"
msgstr "其中有一本很突出。要读一段吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.misc_bookshelf_2.choice.One of them stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.misc_bookshelf_2.choice.One of them stands out. Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "\"Should a merchant not be available in your region, it is always possible to create your own paint by mixing pigments with water.\""
msgstr "“如果您所在的地区没有商家，也可以通过将颜料与水混合来制作自己的颜料。”"

msgid "There's something covered with a drape."
msgstr "有什么东西被帘子遮住了。"

msgid "Remove the drape?"
msgstr "要移开帘子吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.misc_canvas.choice.Remove the drape?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.misc_canvas.choice.Remove the drape?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "Looks like a flat, black square."
msgstr "看起来像个扁平，漆黑的四边形。"

msgid "Take it with you?"
msgstr "要带走吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.misc_canvas.choice.Take it with you?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Wisteria.misc_canvas.choice.Take it with you?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "...It's too large and heavy to carry around."
msgstr "...它太大、太沉了，带不走。"

msgid "A crow stands at the edge of the pool."
msgstr "一只乌鸦站在池子的边缘。"

msgid "A painting with two protruding hands expecting something."
msgstr "一幅画上有两只伸出的手，在乞求着什么。"

msgid "Looks like I can place something on these hands..."
msgstr "看起来我可以把某些东西放在这双手上..."

msgid "A small pool. The water looks clean."
msgstr "一个小水池。水看起来很干净。"
